# 🔹 2) Electricity Bill Calculator

## `App.java`

```java
package com.example;

public class App {

    public double calculateBill(int units) {
        if (units < 0) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Units cannot be negative");
        }

        if (units <= 100) {
            return units * 2;
        } else if (units <= 200) {
            return (100 * 2) + (units - 100) * 3;
        } else {
            return (100 * 2) + (100 * 3) + (units - 200) * 5;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        App bill = new App();
        System.out.println("Bill Amount: " + bill.calculateBill(250));
    }
}
